spanishExample: No toques más, no suena bien.
englishTranslation: Don’t play any more, it doesn’t sound good.

spanishExample: Quiere que toque una canción en la playa.
englishTranslation: He wants me to play a song at the beach.

spanishExample: Te toca ir a la isla.
englishTranslation: It’s your turn to go to the island.

spanishExample: No quieren que toque nada, salvo su propia comida.
englishTranslation: They don’t want him to touch anything, except his own food.

spanishExample: Suenas como un niño, esto no te dolerá.
englishTranslation: You sound like a kid, this won’t hurt you.

spanishExample: Sonó junto a ese árbol.
englishTranslation: It made a sound next to that tree.

spanishExample: Eso no dolió, pero aún podría doler.
englishTranslation: That didn’t hurt, but it still could hurt.

spanishExample: Suenan salvos y felices.
englishTranslation: They sound safe and happy.

spanishExample: No puedes tocar las cosas al lado de esa casa.
englishTranslation: You can’t touch the things beside that house.

spanishExample: No toco nada, y quizás eso suene extraño.
englishTranslation: I don’t play anything, and maybe that sounds strange.

spanishExample: Le tocó ir al bosque.
englishTranslation: It was her turn to go to the forest.

spanishExample: Toque algo para nosotros.
englishTranslation: (Formal) Play something for us.

spanishExample: No creo que pueda sonar bien aquí.
englishTranslation: I don’t think it can sound good here.

spanishExample: ¡No toquen eso! Nadie lo ha tocado.
englishTranslation: (Plural) Don’t touch that! Nobody has touched it.

spanishExample: Toca mi brazo, pero con cuidado porque me duele.
englishTranslation: Touch my arm, but carefully because it hurts me.

spanishExample: Eso no sonaba como un animal.
englishTranslation: That didn’t sound like an animal.

spanishExample: Tú teléfono estaba sonando antes.
englishTranslation: Your phone was ringing before.

spanishExample: No quiero que le duela la cabeza.
englishTranslation: I don’t want her head to hurt.

spanishExample: Va tras sus sueños, pero está a salvo.
englishTranslation: She is going after her dreams, but she is safe.

spanishExample: No estás tocando el sol, eso no es posible.
englishTranslation: You aren’t touching the sun, that’s not possible.

spanishExample: Diles que toquen algo bajo la luna.
englishTranslation: Tell them to play something under the moon.

spanishExample: Siempre tocas algo hermoso.
englishTranslation: You always play something beautiful.
